    <item>
      <title>南非执政党暂停前总统雅各布·祖马的职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/south-africa-s-ruling-party-suspends-former-president-zuma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党非洲人国民大会暂停了前总统雅各布·祖马的职务，因为他表示不会在即将举行的全国选举中投票给非洲人国民大会，而是会支持对手政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/south-africa-s-ruling-party-suspends-former-president-zuma</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非拉马福萨暗示选举临近将提供收入补助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-hints-at-income-grant-as-vote-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨再次暗示引入基本收入补助，并表示尽管该国存在“财政限制”，但仍有“充分的理由”实行这一补助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-hints-at-income-grant-as-vote-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:19:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
